1
00:01:25,330 --> 00:01:29,870
[Coroner's Diary]

2
00:01:30,770 --> 00:01:33,920
[Episode 15]

3
00:01:41,240 --> 00:01:42,330
Young Marshal.

4
00:01:42,330 --> 00:01:44,470
I found no trace of carriages or horses
along the way.

5
00:01:44,470 --> 00:01:46,270
Could they have crossed Mount Yunwu?

6
00:01:46,270 --> 00:01:47,640
They're not fleeting for their lives,

7
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:49,440
so they wouldn't have come to this.

8
00:01:49,440 --> 00:01:50,640
But we've searched the entire forest.

9
00:01:50,640 --> 00:01:52,080
How could there be no trace at all?

10
00:01:52,080 --> 00:01:52,930
Could it be that

11
00:01:52,930 --> 00:01:55,330
they've really grown wings and flown away?

12
00:01:55,610 --> 00:01:58,270
We need to return
to Herbal Garden immediately!

13
00:02:56,900 --> 00:02:57,660
Ning.

14
00:02:58,550 --> 00:02:59,400
Wake up.

15
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:01,290
Ning.

16
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:05,960
Where is this?

17
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:10,440
This is an underground secret chamber.

18
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:14,800
I didn't touch anything.

19
00:03:15,010 --> 00:03:16,820
How did Sun Haoyue manage to do this?

20
00:03:16,820 --> 00:03:18,750
He must have drugged Senior first,

21
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:22,550
then lured us toward his
specially made medicinal incense.

22
00:03:22,550 --> 00:03:24,170
It was my fault. I let my guard down.

23
00:03:24,170 --> 00:03:26,630
He actually went as far as to
use his own junior.

24
00:03:26,630 --> 00:03:27,890
You don't think your senior has...

25
00:03:27,890 --> 00:03:29,290
My senior wouldn't know.

26
00:03:29,610 --> 00:03:31,870
He shouldn't be in any mortal danger now.

27
00:03:34,630 --> 00:03:36,920
Who knows how long we've been here.

28
00:03:37,579 --> 00:03:39,500
Chi should be looking for us by now.

29
00:03:39,500 --> 00:03:40,290
But

30
00:03:40,770 --> 00:03:42,210
no one knows where this secret chamber is.

31
00:03:42,210 --> 00:03:43,960
Even if he wants to rescue us, he can't.

32
00:03:43,960 --> 00:03:45,400
So we need to quickly figure out a way

33
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:46,530
to get out on our own.

34
00:03:47,329 --> 00:03:48,260
Can you stand up?

35
00:03:50,730 --> 00:03:51,450
I can.

36
00:03:51,930 --> 00:03:54,940
I still have great ambitions to
roam the martial world.

37
00:03:54,940 --> 00:03:56,270
I can't be trapped here.

38
00:03:56,730 --> 00:03:57,260
Let's go.

39
00:04:06,930 --> 00:04:07,730
This way.

40
00:05:02,409 --> 00:05:03,350
[Liver]

41
00:05:03,860 --> 00:05:04,610
[Stomach]

42
00:05:08,540 --> 00:05:09,220
[Heart]

43
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:09,610
[Tongue]

44
00:05:09,630 --> 00:05:10,040
[Nose]

45
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:29,120
So he is

46
00:05:29,650 --> 00:05:31,310
the demon of Sanyuan Village?

47
00:05:31,960 --> 00:05:33,690
We can't let him do evil again.

48
00:06:20,360 --> 00:06:21,560
She woke up too early.

49
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:23,320
The dosage was insufficient.

50
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:24,650
How much more should we add?

51
00:06:24,650 --> 00:06:26,300
Sun Haoyue and Bai Feijue?

52
00:06:26,530 --> 00:06:27,530
Add one more mace.

53
00:06:28,000 --> 00:06:30,050
Any more would damage her heart meridian.

54
00:06:30,050 --> 00:06:31,450
Let me know in four hours.

55
00:06:31,610 --> 00:06:32,320
Yes.

56
00:06:39,490 --> 00:06:40,340
Young...

57
00:06:41,050 --> 00:06:42,240
Young Master Bai.

58
00:06:42,850 --> 00:06:43,680
Qin Xiang?

59
00:06:44,000 --> 00:06:45,200
Why?

60
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,460
I had no choice. Your heart

61
00:06:49,490 --> 00:06:51,090
could prolong Madam's life.

62
00:07:04,580 --> 00:07:05,440
Your Highness!

63
00:07:06,000 --> 00:07:06,690
Your Highness!

64
00:07:06,690 --> 00:07:07,710
Something terrible has happened!

65
00:07:07,710 --> 00:07:08,310
What is it?

66
00:07:08,480 --> 00:07:10,260
Her Ladyship asked you to go to
Renxin Clinic immediately.

67
00:07:10,260 --> 00:07:13,120
She also said no one should be allowed
to leave Herbal Garden.

68
00:07:13,120 --> 00:07:13,800
Where is she?

69
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:15,610
Her Ladyship and Her Highness
went to Renxin Clinic

70
00:07:15,610 --> 00:07:17,210
and still haven't come back!

71
00:07:17,440 --> 00:07:18,050
Bai Feng.

72
00:07:18,590 --> 00:07:20,000
Lead a team to seal Herbal Garden

73
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:21,380
and take everyone here to Renxin Clinic.

74
00:07:21,380 --> 00:07:22,450
No one is allowed to enter or leave.

75
00:07:22,450 --> 00:07:23,650
The rest of you, come with me!

76
00:07:23,650 --> 00:07:24,290
Yes!

77
00:07:35,070 --> 00:07:35,710
Come on.

78
00:07:44,970 --> 00:07:45,680
Xiang.

79
00:07:46,440 --> 00:07:47,760
Come on, help her up.

80
00:07:55,810 --> 00:07:57,250
W... Wan?

81
00:07:58,120 --> 00:07:58,760
Young Master Bai...

82
00:07:58,760 --> 00:07:59,530
I know.

83
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:01,620
We'll take you out of here right away.

84
00:08:04,680 --> 00:08:05,610
Those bastards

85
00:08:06,090 --> 00:08:08,820
didn't even leave her
a single piece of clothing.

86
00:08:11,330 --> 00:08:13,390
Xiang, hang in there a little longer.

87
00:08:14,000 --> 00:08:14,490
Here.

88
00:08:16,080 --> 00:08:17,780
Xiang was given a higher dosage than us.

89
00:08:17,780 --> 00:08:19,400
I'm afraid she can't walk for a while.

90
00:08:19,400 --> 00:08:20,600
Let's carry her then.

91
00:08:20,690 --> 00:08:21,370
Let's go.

92
00:08:37,110 --> 00:08:37,840
Let's go.

93
00:09:32,420 --> 00:09:33,150
Are you okay?

94
00:09:33,530 --> 00:09:34,170
I'm okay.

95
00:09:35,540 --> 00:09:36,470
Who would've thought

96
00:09:36,470 --> 00:09:39,070
there'd be a hidden mechanism
under the floor?

97
00:09:41,770 --> 00:09:43,480
There must be an underground river here.

98
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:44,410
Let's turn back.

99
00:09:45,000 --> 00:09:45,600
Okay.

100
00:09:46,390 --> 00:09:46,990
Let's go.

101
00:09:56,260 --> 00:09:59,110
[Benevolent Heart]

102
00:10:06,250 --> 00:10:06,890
Master.

103
00:10:09,830 --> 00:10:12,490
Only these few people are left
in Herbal Garden.

104
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:15,530
Why don't I see Mr. Dong?

105
00:10:16,680 --> 00:10:17,540
Young Marshal.

106
00:10:21,990 --> 00:10:22,850
Young Marshal.

107
00:10:23,010 --> 00:10:24,800
We found this person
outside the inner quarters alone,

108
00:10:24,800 --> 00:10:27,200
lying in the corridor
outside a stone wall.

109
00:10:27,400 --> 00:10:28,400
He's still alive.

110
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:30,080
Fuling,

111
00:10:30,570 --> 00:10:31,800
stay here and look after him.

112
00:10:31,800 --> 00:10:32,410
Yes.

113
00:10:33,890 --> 00:10:35,950
The rest of you, search the backyard!

114
00:10:36,370 --> 00:10:37,200
Yes!

115
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:43,160
Hang in there.

116
00:10:44,800 --> 00:10:45,840
I'm feeling better.

117
00:10:45,840 --> 00:10:47,010
Let me walk on my own.

118
00:10:47,410 --> 00:10:48,170
Thank you.

119
00:10:48,540 --> 00:10:50,000
Nobody is going anywhere.

120
00:10:58,390 --> 00:10:59,670
All of you, get back.

121
00:10:59,950 --> 00:11:00,710
Not a chance!

122
00:11:03,900 --> 00:11:05,480
With your hand shaking like that,

123
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:07,250
do you think your blade can be faster
than my arrow?

124
00:11:07,250 --> 00:11:08,080
Killing you

125
00:11:08,930 --> 00:11:10,260
would be more than easy.

126
00:11:14,250 --> 00:11:16,580
Still overestimating yourself even now.

127
00:11:16,790 --> 00:11:18,080
How amusing.

128
00:11:18,410 --> 00:11:20,480
Why would you do this to me?

129
00:11:20,830 --> 00:11:21,790
Why shouldn't I?

130
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:23,530
Don't tell me

131
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:25,920
you really believed
I was deeply in love with you,

132
00:11:25,920 --> 00:11:27,690
and that I would marry no one but you.

133
00:11:27,690 --> 00:11:29,750
But my feelings for you were genuine.

134
00:11:31,470 --> 00:11:32,710
Genuine?

135
00:11:32,730 --> 00:11:36,170
I think what you have genuine feelings for
is the Bai family's status.

136
00:11:36,170 --> 00:11:37,830
You didn't even know who I was,

137
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:39,500
yet you dared to elope with me.

138
00:11:39,510 --> 00:11:42,050
Your so-called genuine feelings
come rather cheaply.

139
00:11:42,050 --> 00:11:44,480
Seeing how close you three sisters are,

140
00:11:45,840 --> 00:11:47,720
which one should I start with?

141
00:11:49,680 --> 00:11:50,480
You,

142
00:11:52,010 --> 00:11:52,680
you,

143
00:11:55,690 --> 00:11:56,740
or you?

144
00:12:03,370 --> 00:12:05,700
The tea garden has been closed
for so long.

145
00:12:05,720 --> 00:12:08,850
It must be hard to find Senior's
heart source now, right?

146
00:12:08,900 --> 00:12:11,360
Who knows how much longer
Feiyan can hold on?

147
00:12:12,020 --> 00:12:13,750
We may not be able to defeat you,

148
00:12:13,830 --> 00:12:16,330
but harming our own heart meridians
isn't difficult.

149
00:12:16,330 --> 00:12:19,070
If all three of us commit suicide
right in front of you,

150
00:12:19,070 --> 00:12:21,310
I wonder how Senior would punish you.

151
00:12:22,090 --> 00:12:23,330
Suicide?

152
00:12:27,930 --> 00:12:30,290
I don't believe Qin Xiang would dare
to commit suicide!

153
00:12:30,290 --> 00:12:32,430
I just need to wear you down
until you're exhausted,

154
00:12:32,430 --> 00:12:33,830
then I can drag you away.

155
00:12:40,890 --> 00:12:41,600
Stop!

156
00:12:41,870 --> 00:12:43,440
If you dare take one more step forward,

157
00:12:43,440 --> 00:12:44,740
I'll kill Qin Xiang!

158
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:46,630
Let's see what's faster,

159
00:12:46,650 --> 00:12:48,100
your arrow or my dagger?

160
00:12:48,510 --> 00:12:50,080
I'm sure she's told you

161
00:12:50,110 --> 00:12:51,570
how much I can't stand her!

162
00:12:52,250 --> 00:12:53,440
Qin Wan.

163
00:12:53,470 --> 00:12:54,280
And me too.

164
00:12:54,940 --> 00:12:56,210
If Qin Xiang dies,

165
00:12:56,250 --> 00:12:57,580
we'll all die together.

166
00:13:08,850 --> 00:13:10,330
You crazy women!

167
00:13:11,200 --> 00:13:12,800
Have you all lost your minds?

168
00:13:15,760 --> 00:13:17,330
Let her go!

169
00:13:36,730 --> 00:13:38,770
Is... Is he dead?

170
00:13:39,720 --> 00:13:40,890
Dead as he can be.

171
00:13:41,470 --> 00:13:43,530
Even 100 hearts can't bring him back.

172
00:13:44,320 --> 00:13:45,920
He came from that direction,

173
00:13:45,930 --> 00:13:47,570
so the exit must be over there.

174
00:13:47,570 --> 00:13:48,120
Let's go.

175
00:13:54,930 --> 00:13:55,680
Be careful.

176
00:14:07,480 --> 00:14:08,130
Young Marshal.

177
00:14:08,130 --> 00:14:09,410
There's no other way out anywhere.

178
00:14:09,410 --> 00:14:12,010
This stone door must be opened
from the inside.

179
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:15,760
Such massive rocks can't possibly
be moved by human strength alone.

180
00:14:15,760 --> 00:14:16,960
There's no wind here.

181
00:14:17,090 --> 00:14:19,020
It must be hydraulically powered.

182
00:14:19,090 --> 00:14:21,150
But there's no running water around.

183
00:14:22,060 --> 00:14:23,120
Not on the surface,

184
00:14:23,960 --> 00:14:25,790
but that doesn't mean
there isn't any underground.

185
00:14:25,790 --> 00:14:26,790
Start digging!

186
00:15:09,210 --> 00:15:10,240
Someone's coming.

187
00:15:10,240 --> 00:15:12,100
It must be Chi coming to rescue us.

188
00:15:16,120 --> 00:15:17,920
Let's go further inside and see.

189
00:15:55,810 --> 00:15:56,580
This way.

190
00:16:16,150 --> 00:16:17,080
Senior.

191
00:16:31,020 --> 00:16:32,200
Xinlan is dead?

192
00:16:32,960 --> 00:16:34,820
Someone's dead! Someone's dead!

193
00:16:34,840 --> 00:16:35,370
Silence!

194
00:16:36,750 --> 00:16:37,960
Feiyan is not dead.

195
00:16:39,510 --> 00:16:41,370
She's just been sick for too long.

196
00:16:42,050 --> 00:16:42,780
She's tired,

197
00:16:43,530 --> 00:16:44,590
so she fell asleep.

198
00:16:45,170 --> 00:16:46,050
He's gone mad.

199
00:16:46,290 --> 00:16:47,130
I'm not mad.

200
00:16:48,080 --> 00:16:49,250
It's just that you ordinary people

201
00:16:49,250 --> 00:16:51,250
cannot see how beautiful Feiyan is.

202
00:16:51,600 --> 00:16:53,060
If you hadn't interfered,

203
00:16:54,110 --> 00:16:55,190
Feiyan would

204
00:16:56,650 --> 00:16:58,250
certainly be reborn by now.

205
00:16:59,630 --> 00:17:00,440
Don't go.

206
00:17:02,350 --> 00:17:03,190
Senior.

207
00:17:03,890 --> 00:17:05,420
Please come to your senses.

208
00:17:05,650 --> 00:17:06,970
Feiyan is gone.

209
00:17:07,290 --> 00:17:08,550
She's been gone for a long time.

210
00:17:08,550 --> 00:17:10,180
I told you, Feiyan is still alive!

211
00:17:09,359 --> 00:17:14,130
♪ If my tears could speak ♪

212
00:17:11,569 --> 00:17:12,280
As long as

213
00:17:13,960 --> 00:17:16,810
I replace her heart with one from
a young girl full of vital Qi,

214
00:17:14,710 --> 00:17:20,290
♪ If you could hear my heart melt ♪

215
00:17:17,369 --> 00:17:18,780
she will wake up.

216
00:17:19,609 --> 00:17:21,069
She will come back to life.

217
00:17:21,160 --> 00:17:22,710
So you went around killing people?

218
00:17:21,359 --> 00:17:24,710
♪ If I no longer needed ♪

219
00:17:22,960 --> 00:17:24,329
As a physician,

220
00:17:24,410 --> 00:17:25,609
don't you know that

221
00:17:24,730 --> 00:17:27,760
♪ To hold onto the broken dreams ♪

222
00:17:25,609 --> 00:17:26,410
even the freshest heart

223
00:17:26,410 --> 00:17:28,480
cannot revive someone
who has already died?

224
00:17:28,099 --> 00:17:32,630
♪ Maybe then I could finally
let go of regret ♪

225
00:17:35,740 --> 00:17:39,650
♪ Don't sigh for me ♪

226
00:17:37,740 --> 00:17:39,540
My heart transplant technique

227
00:17:39,710 --> 00:17:42,920
♪ Or for the years lost to time ♪

228
00:17:40,870 --> 00:17:43,010
has saved so many lives.

229
00:17:43,290 --> 00:17:50,530
♪ Memories feel just like
the songs I once sang for you ♪

230
00:17:43,500 --> 00:17:44,540
Why?

231
00:17:45,850 --> 00:17:49,050
Why is it that it can't save the one
I love most?

232
00:17:49,730 --> 00:17:50,880
Oh heavens,

233
00:17:50,550 --> 00:17:53,920
♪ I sigh for this deep love
and the broken dreams ♪

234
00:17:52,240 --> 00:17:54,570
why are you so unfair to me!

235
00:17:53,950 --> 00:17:57,170
♪ I sigh for this sorrowful life ♪

236
00:17:54,810 --> 00:17:56,810
This is just your excuse for murder!

237
00:17:57,130 --> 00:17:58,460
Because of your selfish delusions,

238
00:17:57,200 --> 00:18:03,450
♪ Why can't I forget that moonlit night? ♪

239
00:17:59,130 --> 00:18:01,730
how many villagers of Sanyuan Village
have died by your hand,

240
00:18:01,730 --> 00:18:03,950
and how many people have lost
their loved ones because of you?

241
00:18:03,940 --> 00:18:06,440
♪ Don't sigh for me ♪

242
00:18:04,280 --> 00:18:06,280
Have you ever been fair to them?

243
00:18:06,300 --> 00:18:07,540
I've done nothing wrong!

244
00:18:06,460 --> 00:18:09,910
♪ Or for our love song
that's come to an end ♪

245
00:18:08,780 --> 00:18:10,030
The hearts I took

246
00:18:09,930 --> 00:18:17,210
♪ Memories feel just like
the songs I once sang for you ♪

247
00:18:10,480 --> 00:18:12,410
all came from the weak and dying.

248
00:18:13,270 --> 00:18:15,500
They wouldn't have lived
much longer anyway.

249
00:18:15,500 --> 00:18:17,170
Instead of letting these ignorant people

250
00:18:17,170 --> 00:18:18,680
cling to a miserable existence,
wouldn't it be better

251
00:18:17,240 --> 00:18:20,420
♪ I sigh for this deep love
and the broken dreams ♪

252
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:20,910
for them to contribute to
my heart transplant technique?

253
00:18:20,910 --> 00:18:22,840
Wouldn't that benefit the world even more?

254
00:18:21,340 --> 00:18:23,530
♪ I sigh for all the loneliness
in this world ♪

255
00:18:22,880 --> 00:18:24,700
So helping you means benefiting the world,

256
00:18:23,810 --> 00:18:30,280
♪ Even true love
can't resist the passing of time ♪

257
00:18:25,090 --> 00:18:27,330
and refusing you makes them
ignorant commoners?

258
00:18:27,330 --> 00:18:28,260
Who do you think you are,

259
00:18:28,260 --> 00:18:29,020
a god?

260
00:18:29,370 --> 00:18:31,330
How dare you recklessly decide
life and death?

261
00:18:31,330 --> 00:18:32,060
Shame on you!

262
00:18:32,270 --> 00:18:36,050
Crude people like you don't deserve
to follow Feiyan to the netherworld.

263
00:18:36,050 --> 00:18:37,850
But perhaps this is for the best.

264
00:18:37,960 --> 00:18:38,760
The stone gate

265
00:18:39,650 --> 00:18:40,910
has sealed this place.

266
00:18:41,760 --> 00:18:44,620
I believe with your human hearts
accompanying her,

267
00:18:44,810 --> 00:18:47,210
Feiyan is sure to be
healthy and worry-free

268
00:18:47,240 --> 00:18:48,520
in her next life.

269
00:19:05,820 --> 00:19:08,880
In youth, I once wrote poems
on a chrysanthemum pillow.

270
00:19:09,440 --> 00:19:11,880
Collected drafts now locked in cobwebs.

271
00:19:13,170 --> 00:19:16,850
All worldly matters have faded away.

272
00:19:17,510 --> 00:19:21,750
Only the pure fragrance remains
as in old times.

273
00:19:54,810 --> 00:19:55,610
Qin Wan!

274
00:20:15,890 --> 00:20:16,760
Grab onto me!

275
00:20:17,970 --> 00:20:19,010
-Grab tightly!
-Help me!

276
00:20:19,010 --> 00:20:20,060
Don't let go!

277
00:20:20,090 --> 00:20:21,680
