00:38:52,210 --> 00:38:52,770
Here.

564
00:38:54,960 --> 00:38:55,760
What's wrong?

565
00:38:56,040 --> 00:38:58,300
Qin Yan must have discovered something.

566
00:38:58,370 --> 00:39:00,480
We'd better keep our distance from now on.

567
00:39:00,480 --> 00:39:02,410
There's no need to keep it a secret.

568
00:39:02,480 --> 00:39:04,340
They'll find out sooner or later.

569
00:39:04,580 --> 00:39:06,710
You wouldn't want them to be in the dark

570
00:39:06,750 --> 00:39:09,120
when I come to propose in the future,
would you?

571
00:39:09,120 --> 00:39:10,320
Don't talk nonsense.

572
00:39:10,600 --> 00:39:11,920
I'm not talking nonsense.

573
00:39:11,920 --> 00:39:14,120
Though that basement wasn't a nice place,

574
00:39:14,120 --> 00:39:15,850
I meant every word I said there.

575
00:39:20,660 --> 00:39:21,910
But I'm not romantic,

576
00:39:22,290 --> 00:39:23,890
and my temperament is hardly gentle.

577
00:39:23,890 --> 00:39:25,560
If it weren't for my current identity,

578
00:39:25,560 --> 00:39:26,370
I would never want to live

579
00:39:26,370 --> 00:39:28,430
as a proper noble lady bound by rules.

580
00:39:28,440 --> 00:39:31,570
But that's exactly what I love about you,
your defiance.

581
00:39:31,720 --> 00:39:33,180
The woman who can be my wife

582
00:39:33,440 --> 00:39:34,350
should be someone who can

583
00:39:34,350 --> 00:39:36,150
fight alongside me as a heroine,

584
00:39:36,660 --> 00:39:38,210
not someone confined to
the inner chambers,

585
00:39:38,210 --> 00:39:40,670
who only knows to put on makeup
and rely on me.

586
00:39:43,160 --> 00:39:44,560
What wife?

587
00:39:44,880 --> 00:39:47,210
It's still a bit too early
to use that word.

588
00:39:49,520 --> 00:39:50,370
So you're

589
00:39:51,340 --> 00:39:53,210
planning to love me and leave me now?

590
00:39:53,210 --> 00:39:54,170
Love you?

591
00:39:54,190 --> 00:39:55,920
I haven't done anything to you.

592
00:39:56,210 --> 00:39:57,410
Don't talk nonsense.

593
00:39:59,810 --> 00:40:02,670
You've disturbed my peace of mind,
and that counts.

594
00:40:05,000 --> 00:40:06,060
Listen carefully.

595
00:40:06,440 --> 00:40:08,370
Until my Father's name is cleared,

596
00:40:08,850 --> 00:40:10,710
I don't want to discuss marriage.

597
00:40:10,930 --> 00:40:12,850
Because once I become a housewife,

598
00:40:12,850 --> 00:40:15,110
I'll be bound by even more restrictions.

599
00:40:18,890 --> 00:40:19,730
I'm sorry.

600
00:40:20,290 --> 00:40:21,560
If you can't accept this,

601
00:40:21,560 --> 00:40:23,120
we can still go back to
the way things were.

602
00:40:23,120 --> 00:40:23,850
No, we can't.

603
00:40:25,330 --> 00:40:25,960
Why not?

604
00:40:28,370 --> 00:40:30,770
Because my heart
can't go back to how it was,

605
00:40:31,160 --> 00:40:32,090
and also because

606
00:40:32,250 --> 00:40:35,020
I've always intended for you to be

607
00:40:35,290 --> 00:40:37,950
my Crown Prince openly
with your true identity.

608
00:40:46,600 --> 00:40:47,440
Yan Chi.

609
00:40:48,730 --> 00:40:49,480
However...

610
00:40:51,080 --> 00:40:54,010
However, you'll need to give me
something in return.

611
00:40:55,000 --> 00:40:56,160
What do you want?

612
00:40:59,330 --> 00:41:00,930
In Jingzhou, there's Yue Qing;

613
00:41:00,930 --> 00:41:02,730
and at Medicine King Valley, there are
your fellow disciples.

614
00:41:02,730 --> 00:41:03,690
Once you go to the capital,

615
00:41:03,690 --> 00:41:06,160
what if you encounter people
with ill intentions?

616
00:41:06,160 --> 00:41:07,770
To prevent any unexpected troubles,

617
00:41:07,770 --> 00:41:09,570
shouldn't you give me something

618
00:41:09,960 --> 00:41:11,160
to put my mind at ease?

619
00:41:12,160 --> 00:41:13,690
But I have nothing of value.

620
00:41:13,810 --> 00:41:16,740
Even Hanyue and the Nine Needles
were gifts from you.

621
00:41:37,730 --> 00:41:39,040
Then you must promise me,

622
00:41:39,040 --> 00:41:41,040
no concubines, no secondary wives.

623
00:41:41,290 --> 00:41:42,710
Whether we're married or not,

624
00:41:42,710 --> 00:41:44,300
if you cannot be faithful to me alone,

625
00:41:44,300 --> 00:41:45,730
then vast as the mountains and seas are,

626
00:41:45,730 --> 00:41:47,190
I can go anywhere I please.

627
00:41:55,480 --> 00:41:56,290
Qin Wan.

628
00:41:56,690 --> 00:41:58,550
I, Yan Chi, am not a fickle person.

629
00:41:59,440 --> 00:42:00,560
It was on the battlefield

630
00:42:00,560 --> 00:42:02,640
that I learned what it means
to face life and death together

631
00:42:02,640 --> 00:42:04,000
and to make a lifelong promise.

632
00:42:04,000 --> 00:42:06,570
The path we've chosen is long
and full of obstacles.

633
00:42:06,570 --> 00:42:07,590
Aside from you,

634
00:42:07,970 --> 00:42:10,240
no other woman can walk it alongside me.

635
00:42:11,890 --> 00:42:14,890
To have you in this lifetime
is all I could ever ask for.

636
00:42:18,110 --> 00:42:22,700
♪ Having walked alone through
wind and rain for years ♪

637
00:42:22,890 --> 00:42:26,130
♪ Never having encountered this love ♪

638
00:42:26,920 --> 00:42:30,980
♪ Until you came to my world ♪

639
00:42:31,020 --> 00:42:34,490
♪ And wrote our destined bond ♪

640
00:42:34,940 --> 00:42:38,400
♪ The sunshine you gave me ♪

641
00:42:38,660 --> 00:42:42,080
♪ Painted pictures of the future ♪

642
00:42:42,960 --> 00:42:47,000
♪ Only when I drew near to you
did I realize ♪

643
00:42:47,100 --> 00:42:50,580
♪ This love was already deep and endless ♪

644
00:43:00,290 --> 00:43:02,420
Master, I have something to report...

645
00:43:10,000 --> 00:43:10,970
What's wrong with my eyes?

646
00:43:10,970 --> 00:43:12,580
Why can't I see anything all of a sudden?

